<section id="home-section-1"> <div class="container">
<h1 class="text-center">Welcome to the start of your perfect <span>Wedding Planning Journey</span></h1>

<p class="lead text-center">We offer a professional wedding planning service for couples who have chosen the beautiful island of Mallorca as a dream wedding destination.</p>
</div>

<div class="container three-sec-flex-opac">
<div class="row">
<div class="col-md-4 col-sm-6 col-xs-12 aos-init aos-animate" data-aos="fade-left" data-aos-duration="2000">
<div class="elementBackgroundImage-1">
<div class="opac-bg">
<div><img alt="Bespoke Wedding Planning" src="/assets/images/icons/home/Bespoke-icon.png?9" /></div>

<p class="text-center">Bespoke Wedding Planning</p>

<div>
<ul>
	<li>A fully personalised planning service</li>
	<li>Designed 100% to your specifications</li>
	<li>We manage all elements but at the same time you are still in control</li>
	<li>Be involved as much or as little as you like</li>
</ul>
</div>

<div class="box-button"><a class="btn btn-pink" href="/en/services-prices" title="Bespoke Wedding Planning">Full Details</a></div>
</div>
</div>
</div>

<div class="col-md-4 col-sm-6 col-xs-12 aos-init aos-animate" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-duration="2000">
<div class="elementBackgroundImage-2">
<div class="opac-bg">
<div><img alt="Affordable Wedding  Packages" src="/assets/images/icons/home/Vow-renewals.png?9" /></div>

<p class="text-center">Affordable Wedding Packages</p>

<div>
<ul>
	<li>3 tiers of easy to choose packages </li>
	<li>A great choice of carefully selected venues </li>
	<li>Fully inclusive – all you need for a perfect day</li>
	<li>Only our best suppliers </li>
	<li>Optional add-ons & upgrades available</li>
</ul>
</div>

<div class="box-button"><a class="btn btn-pink" href="/en/wedding-packages" title="Affordable Wedding Packages">Show me</a></div>
</div>
</div>
</div>

<div class="col-md-4 col-sm-6 col-xs-12 aos-init aos-animate" data-aos="fade-right" data-aos-duration="2000">
<div class="elementBackgroundImage-3">
<div class="opac-bg">
<div><img alt="Wedding Day Management" src="/assets/images/icons/home/Wedding-coordination-500x500.png?8" /></div>

<p class="text-center">Wedding Day Management</p>

<div>
<ul class="innerList defaultList custom-list">
	<li>On-the-day only Wedding Coordination</li>
	<li>You plan your big day and we step in for the final 48 hours</li>
	<li>Relax & enjoy your day</li>
	<li>Complete peace of mind</li>
	<li>Professional, experienced & friendly coordinators</li>
</ul>
</div>

<div class="box-button"><a class="btn btn-pink" href="/en/on-the-day-coordination" title="Wedding Day Management">More Details</a></div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div></section><section id="home-section-2"> <div class="parallax">

</div></section><section id="home-section-3"> <div class="container-fluid text-center mt5">
  <span data-aos="fade-up"
     data-aos-duration="2000">LET’S GET ACQUAINTED…</span>
  <div class="section-header">
    <h2>Your Mallorca Wedding Planners </h2>
  </div>
  <p>Our team has organised hundreds of Mallorca weddings.</p>
  <p>Our vast wedding planning experience combined with 20 years of local Mallorca knowledge gained as full-time residents, means our expertise is second to none. </p>
</div></section><section id="home-section-grid"> <div class="container">
  <div class="row row1">
    <div class="text-center" data-aos="fade-up"
     data-aos-duration="2000">
      <h3 class="title">Why Choose Us?</h3>
    </div>
    <div class="row row-no-gutters">
      <div class="col-xs centered col-sm-6 no_padding border_right">
        <h3 data-aos="fade-right"><span>Weddings</span> Are Our Passion!</h3>
        <div class="bordered">
          <p class="p_left"> You are not a number, a pay cheque or just a client. We genuinely give 100%
            dedication to each
            and every one of the weddings in Mallorca that we are lucky enough to be a part of. </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-xs centered col-sm-6 no_padding">
        <h3 class="right" data-aos="fade-left">We Are A <span>Partnership</span></h3>
        <div class="bordered">
          <p class="p_right"> Many wedding planners in Mallorca operate on their own, however we are a partnership
            meaning you get
            double the help and support – one of us is always available! </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="row row-no-gutters">
      <div class="col-xs centered col-sm-6 no_padding border_right">
        <h3 data-aos="fade-right">Available On <span>Whatsapp</span>, <span>Messenger</span> <span>Skype</span> & <span>Facetime</span></h3>
        <div class="bordered">
          <p class="p_left"> Most of our couples are based outside of Mallorca and we understand the
            difficulty of trying to plan your wedding from afar, therefore we are always available via
            email, Whatsapp, Messenger, Skype and Facetime – however you want to communicate is fine
            with us! </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-xs centered col-sm-6 no_padding">
        <h3 class="right" data-aos="fade-left">Based Here <span>On The Island Full Time</span></h3>
        <div class="bordered">
          <p class="p_right"> We don’t flit back and forth and so our knowledge and expertise plus the
            level of dedication to your planning time here on the island is 100%. </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="row row-no-gutters">
      <div class="col-xs centered col-sm-6 no_padding border_right">
        <h3 data-aos="fade-right">We Speak <span>Your Language</span></h3>
        <div class="bordered">
          <p class="p_left"> Both business partners are UK expats so your language is our language. We are
            fluent in Spanish too, so communicating with local venues and suppliers on your behalf is
            done with ease. </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-xs centered col-sm-6 no_padding">
        <h3 class="right" data-aos="fade-left">20 Years' Local <span>Knowledge Of Mallorca</span></h3>
        <div class="bordered">
          <p class="p_right"> We have two decades of local knowledge of Mallorca - we know all the venues
            and all the suppliers and so are able to advise you to make the best choices possible for
            your big day. Access to our “White Hot Book” is priceless. </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="row row-no-gutters">
      <div class="col-xs centered col-sm-6 no_padding border_right">
        <h3 data-aos="fade-right">In-House Wedding <span>Stylist</span> & <span>Florist</span></h3>
        <div class="bordered">
          <p class="p_left"> We have an in-house wedding stylist and florist meaning that the styling and
            planning of your wedding runs seamlessly together.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-xs centered col-sm-6 no_padding">
        <h3 class="right" data-aos="fade-left">In-House <span>Celebrant</span> & <span>Expert Advice</span></h3>
        <div class="bordered">
          <p class="p_right">We have an in-house celebrant meaning that you will get expert advice
            throughout your experience with us on the legal aspects of your ceremony, your paperwork
            back in your home country, your vows and the type of ceremony you would like. </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div></section><section id="home-section-5"> <div class="parallax">
  <div class="flex_box">
    <div class="text_box">
      <div class="container-fluid text-center mt5 mb5">
        <h2>Our Couples' Kind Words</h2>
        <span>HOW OUR HAPPY COUPLES FELT</span> <span>ABOUT THEIR MALLORCA WEDDING</span>
        <div class="container-fluid">
          <div id="carousel" class="carousel slide" data-ride="carousel">
            <div class="carousel-inner">
              <div class="item active">
                <div class="row">
                  <div class="col-xs-12">
                    <div class="caption">
                      <p class="text-info lead">
                      <blockquote class="testimonial_quote">"It was the best decision we
                        made to have
                        Olivia help us
                        with the wedding. Nothing was too much trouble and she saved us
                        both so much
                        time to concentrate on just enjoying ourselves. We can't thank
                        you enough for
                        all your help and hard work. Couldn't have asked for anything
                        better."
                        <p class="clients">Tara & Frazier</p>
                      </blockquote>
                      </p>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="item">
                <div class="row">
                  <div class="col-xs-12">
                    <div class="caption">
                      <p class="text-info lead">
                      <blockquote class="testimonial_quote">"Our big day was absolutely
                        perfect, our
                        planner remained calm and focused throughout and ensured that
                        every single one
                        of our guests had a great time. We received many compliments on
                        not only how
                        beautiful things were, but also how smoothly and professionally
                        everything was
                        done. We would without a doubt, recommend A White Hot Wedding to
                        any bride &
                        groom, so if you're considering booking a wedding planner, look
                        no further and
                        just do it, we promise you won't regret it!”
                        <p class="clients">Rhiannon & Jack</p>
                      </blockquote>
                      </p>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="item">
                <div class="row">
                  <div class="col-xs-12">
                    <div class="caption">
                      <p class="text-info lead">
                      <blockquote class="testimonial_quote">"Our wedding ceremony and
                        reception was perfect and everything we dreamed of. All our
                        guests enjoyed it. We didn't want our day to end. You were the
                        perfect host and handled everything professionally. The club was
                        a beautiful venue we thoroughly recommend it. Thank you for a
                        beautiful wedding and memories we will cherish forever."
                        <p class="clients">Donna & Christian</p>
                      </blockquote>
                      </p>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="item">
                <div class="row">
                  <div class="col-xs-12">
                    <div class="caption">
